description: TrStSaCellProfile: Table storing Ericsson-specific attributes of a cell profile, including its identifier, location, configuration details, and timestamps.  Columns: dateTime (Timestamp of data recording), Area_Name (Geographic area of the cell), CellId (Unique cell identifier), Id2 (Duplicate of CellId), Id3 (Unknown identifier), Id4 (Unknown identifier, likely default value), vsDataType (Data type identifier), vsDataFormatVersion (Version of data format), TrStSaCellProfile.userLabel (User-defined label), TrStSaCellProfile.trStSaCellProfileId (Profile identifier), TrStSaCellProfile.reservedBy (Reserved field), TrStSaCellProfile.ueConfGroupType (UE configuration group type).
queries: Show me all TrStSaCellProfile entries where Area_Name is 'Downtown' and dateTime is within the last 24 hours.
What is the ueConfGroupType for CellId 12345?
Find all TrStSaCellProfile entries with vsDataFormatVersion < 2.0.
Retrieve the TrStSaCellProfile.userLabel for all cells in Area_Name 'SuburbA'  where  TrStSaCellProfile.trStSaCellProfileId starts with 'ABC'.
How many distinct Area_Name values exist in the TrStSaCellProfile table for vsDataType = 'LTE'?
